    size=&quot;2&quot;>&lt;strong>&lt;em>A Simplified Approach to IT Architecture with BPMN - A Coherent Methodology for Modeling Every&#xD;
    Level of the Enterprise&lt;/em>&lt;/strong>.&lt;/font> See the cover below.&#xD;
